node.text: From investment banking to video games, Andy Wilson successfully made his dream transition to development. This week’s episode of Press F Podcast is a must-listen for anyone interested in video games as a career -- balancing theory with practical knowledge. Available now on Spotify and Apple.

node.title: Advice to those Interesting in Entering the Video Game Industry

node.text: Say hi to our new look 👀

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sledgehammer Games on June 19, 2021 tagging @_sashamufasa_. May be a cartoon of 2 people, footwear and text.

node.text:
In commemoration of #Juneteenth, our team partnered with local Bay Area artist, @_sashamufasa_, to create a special piece of art, gifted as a shirt to our devs.

Today we’re also passing the microphone to some of our black game developers to share their thoughts & experiences. You can find those employee spotlights on LinkedIn & Twitter at LifeAtSHG.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sledgehammer Games on June 01, 2021. May be a cartoon of text that says 'pride 2021 @anniepartick HAMMER LGAMES'.

node.text:
Happy #Pride Month!

Artist Annie Partick is helping us celebrate in style this month with a social media visual takeover! We appreciate Annie's art and are excited about this collaboration. For more of Annie, visit her Artstation or Twitter via 🔎, “AnniePartick".

For more Pride updates and content, follow us on Twitter at @LifeatSHG.
